      },
      {
        "children": [
          {
            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "One potential explanation for the parts shortages for GM is the automaker’s continued insistence its suppliers to sign off on an Environmental, Social, and Governance Partnership Pledge (ESG). GM wouldn’t say just how many of its vast network of suppliers had signed up last year, which you can read more about ",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          },
          {
            "children": [
              {
                "detail": 0,
                "format": 0,
                "mode": "normal",
                "style": "",
